                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Et malgré que les jours soient beaux comme un beau songe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Cette heure qui me plaît, je l’attends trop longtemps.",
