                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Dans le désir et le regret de la nuit douce",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6−6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Par ces longs soirs d’été trop lumineux, allons…",
